122
00:06:33,476 --> 00:06:35,277
<i>The army has needs.</i>

123
00:06:35,311 --> 00:06:37,678
The city's population will have tripled.

124
00:06:40,182 --> 00:06:42,921
Why are you so anxious to go to New York?

125
00:06:45,191 --> 00:06:47,993
Don't you want to celebrate
Christmas with your family,

126
00:06:48,027 --> 00:06:49,328
with your wife and child?

127
00:06:49,363 --> 00:06:53,167
Of course I do, but, uh...

128
00:06:53,201 --> 00:06:54,967
I must provide for them first.

129
00:06:55,001 --> 00:06:56,868
Well, if it's a question of a loan...

130
00:06:56,903 --> 00:06:59,136
<i>- No.
- ... to get you through the winter.</i>

131
00:06:59,171 --> 00:07:00,738
<i>- I don't want...
- Mary doesn't have to know.</i>

132
00:07:00,772 --> 00:07:03,040
I want nothing from you.

133
00:07:06,908 --> 00:07:08,874
