137
00:07:17,209 --> 00:07:20,144
I call it my duty and I would do it again.

138
00:07:20,178 --> 00:07:23,245
Well, good. You still have your
wife's gravestone to tear out.

139
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:36,484
She would know you didn't mean that.

140
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:39,954
