want nothing from me is untrue.

141
00:07:41,389 --> 00:07:45,957
You want my pass to the
city and I do not grant it

142
00:07:45,991 --> 00:07:49,858
<i>because I know that you
running from your home,</i>

143
00:07:49,893 --> 00:07:53,432
