144
00:07:57,900 --> 00:08:00,730
I will be celebrating
Christmas at my house this year,

145
00:08:00,765 --> 00:08:03,597
with my family.

146
00:08:03,632 --> 00:08:05,432
Don't expect us.

147
00:08:59,856 --> 00:09:02,656
