176
00:10:26,572 --> 00:10:27,873
It's, uh...

177
00:10:27,907 --> 00:10:31,413
uh, Abigail, is it?

178
00:10:33,115 --> 00:10:36,214
All right.

179
00:10:45,723 --> 00:10:47,291
It was your father's.

180
00:10:50,394 --> 00:10:53,028
He'd have been so proud that you can read.

181
